      "widgets_values": [
        "{\"version\":1,\"content\":\"<h2>MODELS AND NODES USED IN THIS WORKFLOW</h2><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #777777\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3></h3><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"CLIP\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Load CLIP</h3><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\"><a class=\\\"pix-note-dl\\\" style=\\\"background-color: #f66744\\\" href=\\\"https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/gemma-4/resolve/main/text_encoders/gemma4_e4b_it_fp8_scaled.safetensors\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\">Download gemma4_e4b_it_fp8_scaled.safetensors<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnsize\\\">8.06 GB</span></a></span>&nbsp;\\n\\n</p><div class=\\\"pix-note-folderhint\\\" style=\\\"color: #888888\\\">Place in: ComfyUI/models/text_encoders</div><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #777777\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3></h3><p>\\n\\n</p><h3></h3><p>\\n\\n</p><p><span data-ic=\\\"warning-v1\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;After placing the files, <span style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">restart</span> ComfyUI or refresh model lists using <span style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\">R</span> shortcut.</p><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #777777\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"nodes-installed\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Custom Nodes</h3><p>\\n\\n</p><ul>\\n  <li>Pixaroma</li>\\n</ul><p>\\n\\n</p><hr class=\\\"pix-note-hr-solid\\\" style=\\\"color: #777777\\\"><p>\\n\\n</p><h3><span data-ic=\\\"pixaroma\\\" class=\\\"pix-note-ic\\\" contenteditable=\\\"false\\\" style=\\\"color: #f66744\\\"></span>&nbsp;Resources</h3><p>\\n\\n<span class=\\\"pix-note-btnblock\\\">\\n  <a class=\\\"pix-note-discord\\\" href=\\\"https://discord.com/invite/gggpkVgBf3\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\